high_descs: After turning around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the table.
Pick up dish sponge from the table.
Turn around and walk to the counter top to your left.
Place dish sponge on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Shifting dish sponge from one place to another.

high_descs: Turn right and then turn right to the sink.
Pick the dish sponge near the sink.
Place the dish sponge on the countertop.
anns.task_desc: To place the dish sponge on the countertop.

high_descs: Walk to the sink after turning around in the kitchen.
remove the dish sponge from the sink.
Move toward the countertop with the dish sponge.
move the dish sponge to a different spot on the counter.
anns.task_desc: remove the dish sponge and set it in a different location on the counter.
